author: @allisondeliva
text: “TWICE holds the entire top 4 highest-grossing concerts by female groups in the US with concerts performed in Inglewood and New York City as part of the "III Tour".” Whenever they achieved something that no other female group or artist has achieved, I feel so proud. They deserve it and they worked hard for it. TWICE already prove themselves and still proving how great artists they are around the world. ONCEs are always proud of what they've achieved.

author: @allisondeliva
text: “TWICE earns the most-attended concerts by female Asian acts in the US with 13,384 tickets sold each night played at the UBS Arena in New York City on February 26-27.” Another achievement for this year and it's not just a normal achievement because it's the whole Female Asian Act. TWICE are really growing and growing. I love to witness how they're becoming more successful. They're truly legends and no one can stop them to become more successful and bigger worldwide.
